instructions: Put the dinner plate on the table cloth.
Put the salad plate on top of the dinner plate.
Put the napkin on top of the salad plate.
Put the wine glass at the top right side of the table cloth.
Put the water glass to the right of the wine glass.
Put the salad fork on the right side of the dinner plate.
Put the dinner fork to the right of the salad fork.
Put the knife to the left of the dinner plate.
Put the spoon to the left of the knife.
